            "id": 72120,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Que montre ce code dans la console ?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" fullName = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Jane&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"fullName = fullName + \" /><text value=\"&quot; Bowling&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(fullName);\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Jane Bowling\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>Jane Bowling</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>Bowling Jane</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\"><code>Jane Bowling</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Assigning a value",
            "id": 72122,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Assigne <code>15</code> à la variable <code>wallet</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" wallet = \" /><text value=\"15\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"13\" endIndex=\"14\" /><option startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"17\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"===\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>=</code> suivi de <code>15</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Self-assigning a value",
            "id": 72123,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Donne à <code>likes</code> une valeur de sorte que <code>5</code> s'affiche dans la console.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" number = \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" likes = number;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(likes);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"30\" endIndex=\"36\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"6\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"7\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"5\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>number</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Incrementing numbers",
            "id": 72124,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Ajoute cinq à la valeur de la variable <code>inventory</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" inventory = \" /><text value=\"11\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"inventory = inventory + \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(inventory);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"32\" endIndex=\"45\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"5\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"16\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>inventory + 5</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Why self-assigning matters",
            "id": 72125,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Soustrais un de la valeur de la variable <code>cards</code>, puis ajoute quatre.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" cards = \" /><text value=\"3\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"cards = cards - \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"cards = cards + \" /><text value=\"4\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(cards);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"29\" endIndex=\"30\" /><option startIndex=\"31\" endIndex=\"32\" /><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"49\" /><option startIndex=\"50\" endIndex=\"51\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"6\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>-</code> suivi de <code>1</code> puis <code>+</code>, <code>4</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
